videos.description: Clemson's Aliyah Collier turns the ball over, leading to Lindsay Allen's nice spin move for two points.
videos.headline: Early Clemson turnover leads to fast break points for Notre Dame

videos.description: Tigers' guard Aliyah Collier finds teammate Kobi Thornton under the basket for the tough And-1 play.
videos.headline: Clemson's Thornton gets the layup, plus the foul

videos.description: Fighting Irish forward Kristina Nelson comes up with a big block that leads to a transition layup for Lindsay Allen.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Nelson's block leads to a transition lay-in

videos.description: Tigers' Kobi Thornton corrals the loose ball to get the lay-in, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Clemson's Thornton pulls the tigers to within seven after the tough layup and the foul

videos.description: Clemson's Kobi Thornton notches another And-1 layup to pull the Tigers to within single digits.
videos.headline: Tigers' Thornton ends a fast break with another And-1

videos.description: Tigers' forward Nelly Perry gets the bounce to make it a two point game vs. Notre Dame late.
videos.headline: Perry pulls Clemson to within two late
